gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 112, Wizards 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pacers defeated the Wizards, 112-104. Myles Turner led seven Pacers in double-figures with 18 points and 13 rebounds as Bruce Brown (16 points, nine rebounds, six assists) and Bennedict Mathurin (16 points, seven rebounds) totaled 32 points. Jordan Poole led the Wizards in the loss with 28 points, four rebounds, and seven assists.
